ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/Ynr7-fTGOXNX0GV4VZHMnUnZHUY=/768x960/filters:format(webp)/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg, https://images.food52.com/tpjq2gZlA5j6OD8YpEQJEOTIhm4=/1536x1920/filters:format(webp)/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/yppWeJRgN37bCi2PgySBWIlTrGs=/768x960/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg, https://images.food52.com/SlXEXEYT_C7a-HVhaUspfDKRyXY=/1536x1920/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/2EUpi5V2sx8zSx3OMntz3-er9jE=/375x468/filters:format(webp)/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg, https://images.food52.com/-4JxhcgyLpWe22yV78yYZslM7y4=/750x936/filters:format(webp)/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/7ngBVTElo2Zf9V88O_AWShX66Bs=/375x468/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg, https://images.food52.com/QsuEDGLIr3nXxb4MQmDaO9A4IQs=/750x936/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"1205\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/7ngBVTElo2Zf9V88O_AWShX66Bs=/375x468/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg, https://images.food52.com/QsuEDGLIr3nXxb4MQmDaO9A4IQs=/750x936/dd97db74-3f32-45d3-b2ab-692067044324--SECTION4.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003e5. Bring the Chatterbox\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eGot a friend who’s never met an awkward silence? Make sure they’re at the top of the guest list—and have them arrive a little early. If you’re doing assigned seating, put them smack in the middle to help bridge groups. As Julia puts it (à la Curb Your Enthusiasm), your “middler” should be the strongest conversationalist with the best stories to tell.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003ch2\u003e6. Be Prepared\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eAs the host, be ready to jump in and smooth over any lulls with a tailored conversation starter. If you already know what your guests have in common—great. If not, throw out one of these: celebrity encounters or their Kevin Bacon number from Beyoncé, their most cancellable food take, or how they’d describe themselves as a charcuterie board ingredient.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n              \u003ccenter\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eWhat are your best tips for breaking the ice around a dinner table?\u003c/em\u003e\n\u003c/center\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
